tion should operate.</div><div><br></div><div>I urge YouTube to acknowledge this issue and take meaningful steps toward transparency and fairness in its content distribution.</div><div><br></div><div>Democracy should not be decided by who can afford to be seenâ€”it should be about ensuring that every voter has access to the full range of political choices available to them.</div><div><br></div><div>Sincerely,</div><div>Wendell</div><div>Candidate for Prime Minister of Australia</div><div>Emergence Party</div><div>ğŸ”— wendellsdiary.com</div>
